me.taylorkelly.mywarp.dataconnections

Class EventConnectionBridge

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.taylorkelly.mywarp.dataconnections.EventConnectionBridge

  • public class EventConnectionBridge
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides a bridge between the various WarpEvent implementations and a DataConnection, transforming relevant events into calls on the data-connection.
